text: Islambakhty () is a rural locality (a selo) in Tarkazinsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 446 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 50 km from Yermekeyevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Islambakhty
